01:28:53,440 --> 01:28:57,960
<i>Povezanost srca, draga moja,</i>

1137
01:28:58,040 --> 01:29:02,760
<i>ako se smanji sutra..</i>

1138
01:29:02,880 --> 01:29:07,440
<i>Čak i ako se uslovi pogoršaju..</i>

1139
